fields.description: Attach your hair extension using Liquid Gold glue. The glue is best suited for inserting hair bridles. 30ml.

fields.name: Wig Stand
fields.description: Are you tired of your wig having to be fixed and combed even before you put it on? With the Rapunzel Wig Stand you avoid the unnecessary tangle, the wig keeps its nice hairstyle and is ready to use whenever you want!

fields.name: Quick & Easy - double-sided tape
fields.description: 8 pieces with double-sided tape. Works for inserting and reusing your Quick & Easy hair extensions. Size: 4cm width, 1cm height

fields.name: Poze Tape Remover
fields.description: Poze Tape Remover is a removal liquid for Tape-on extensions. Gentle and effective removal of all types of extension tape. 50ml.

fields.name: Poze Removing Plier
fields.description: Pliers for removal. Use the pliers together with the remover to remove keratin wax loops. Also used for clamping and clamping away micro rings or for clamping to Tape-on extensions

fields.name: Clip-on clips
fields.description: Clip-on clips. 3 cm long, 10 pcs/pack, 3 holes in each for a secure attachment. Protective silicone surface for gentle insertion of your Clip-on set.
